-- Spain banks could need more public money: official
-- 
-- Fri Apr 27, 2012 5:40am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/04/27/us-spain-economy-banks-idUSBRE83Q0E020120427

 

 MADRID  (Reuters) - Spanish banks could need more public money, Spain's Economy Secretary Fernando Jimenez Latorre said on Friday, but he ruled out the use of European funds to bail out lenders. 
 (Reporting By Feliciano Tisera; Editing by Sonya Dowsett)